
<!doctype html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
<title>Sürpriz Sayfa</title>
<style>
  body {
    margin:0;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,#0b1020 0%, #0f1730 100%);
    color:#eef0f6;
    min-height:100vh;
    padding:24px;
  }
  .lock-wrap { max-width:800px; margin:auto; text-align:center; }
  .pw { padding:12px; font-size:16px; }
  button { padding:12px; }
  .content { display:none; }
  .gallery { margin-top:20px; }
  .photo-block { margin:20px 0; }
  .photo-block img { max-width:100%; border-radius:10px; }
  .caption { margin-top:8px; font-size:18px; color:#ffd1dc; }
  .heart-area { margin-top:30px; text-align:center; }
  .heart { font-size:100px; animation:beat 1s infinite; color:red; }
  @keyframes beat {
    0%{transform:scale(.95)}
    50%{transform:scale(1.05)}
    100%{transform:scale(.95)}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="lock-wrap">
  <div id="lockView">
    <h2>💌 Sadece bizim için 💌</h2>
    <p>Şifreyi gir sevgilim:</p>
    <input id="pw" class="pw" type="password" placeholder="Şifre"/>
    <button onclick="unlock()">Aç</button>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:gray">İpucu: Sevgili olduğumuz o güzel gün</p>
  </div>

  <div id="content" class="content">
    <div class="gallery">
      <div class="photo-block">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="foto1"/>
        <div class="caption">Senin kollarında huzuru buldum 🤍</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-block">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="foto2"/>
        <div class="caption">Her anın parlayan yıldızı sensin ✨</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-block">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="foto3"/>
        <div class="caption">Gülüşün ömrümün en güzel melodisi 💫</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="heart-area">
      <div class="heart">❤</div>
      <div style="font-size:20px;margin-top:10px;">Kalbim hep senin için atacak</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
const PASSWORDS = ["2023-12-01","01.12.2023","01122023","1.12.2023"];
function unlock() {
  const val = document.getElementById('pw').value.trim();
  if (PASSWORDS.includes(val)) {
    document.getElementById('lockView').style.display='none';
    document.getElementById('content').style.display='block';
  } else {
    alert("Yanlış şifre 😕");
  }
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
